<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1">
  <meta http-equiv="refresh" content="900">  <!-- self-refresh every 15 min -->
  <title>{{ title }} · Hub4Apps Market Intel</title>
  {% set rp = root_path | default("") %}
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="{{ rp }}styles.css">
</head>
<body>
  <header>
    <div class="brand">
      <span class="logo">📈</span>
      <h1>Hub4Apps Market Intel</h1>
      <span class="subtitle">private · educational · not financial advice</span>
    </div>
    <nav>
      <a href="{{ rp }}index.html"     class="{% if active=='index' %}active{% endif %}">Dashboard</a>
      <a href="{{ rp }}signals.html"   class="{% if active=='signals' %}active{% endif %}">Signals</a>
      <a href="{{ rp }}events.html"    class="{% if active=='events' %}active{% endif %}">Events</a>
      <a href="{{ rp }}agents.html"    class="{% if active=='agents' %}active{% endif %}">Agents</a>
      <a href="{{ rp }}backtest.html"  class="{% if active=='backtest' %}active{% endif %}">Backtest</a>
      <a href="{{ rp }}paper_trades.html" class="{% if active=='paper_trades' %}active{% endif %}">Paper Trades</a>
      <a href="{{ rp }}learning.html"  class="{% if active=='learning' %}active{% endif %}">Learning</a>
    </nav>
    <div class="meta">
      <span>generated {{ generated_at }} UTC</span>
    </div>
  </header>
  <main>
    {% block content %}{% endblock %}
  </main>
  <footer>
    <p>v1 paper-trading vocabulary: <strong>WATCH</strong> / <strong>RESEARCH</strong> / <strong>AVOID_CHASE</strong> / <strong>CHASE_RISK</strong>.
    Phase 6A paper forecasts use <strong>PAPER_LONG</strong> / <strong>PAPER_WATCH</strong> / <strong>PAPER_AVOID</strong> / <strong>NO_TRADE</strong>.
    The bot does not say BUY or SELL until 60 days of paper-trading hits the §17.6 graduation thresholds.</p>
    <p>Data: SEC EDGAR · trumpstruth.org RSS · yfinance. Free-tier stack: GitHub Actions + Supabase Free + Hostinger static.</p>
  </footer>
</body>
</html>
